          <br>
          The system routes such chats of customers on priority who have re-initiated the chat on the same day and whose chats have been queued to the same queue.</p>
        </td>
       </tr>
       <tr>
        <th>
         <p>Queue Waiting Time and Queue Position</p>
        </th>
